    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Talking About Race</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Rosellen Storm letter on series about race relations in America notes she is saving July 16 issue for her granddaughters</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I am putting this issue (July 16) away with other important things I hope my granddaughters learn about in the future. As a child of the 60's, my generation was supposed to make a difference. We didn't do enough. Maybe my granddaughters and the children of the new century will.</p>
        <p>Rosellen Storm  Southold, N.Y.</p>
      </block>
